# Implement Dashboard Profile Navigation

## Goal Description
Link the “الملف الشخصي” item in the topbar user dropdown to navigate to `/dashboard/profile` without modifying any backend endpoints. A new client-only profile page will be created to display the user's details.

## Proposed Changes

### Client Application
#### [MODIFY] [DashboardLayout.tsx](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/components/layout/DashboardLayout.tsx)
- Update the `DropdownMenuItem` for "الملف الشخصي" to call `navigate('/dashboard/profile')`. By default, the `DropdownMenu` component in shadcn closes automatically when an item is selected.

#### [NEW] [ProfilePage.tsx](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/pages/dashboard/ProfilePage.tsx)
- Create a new client-side route component `ProfilePage` that utilizes `useAuthStore` to fetch the current user's details.
- Render a clean card layout displaying:
  - Full Name
  - Email
  - Role
  - Last Login (if present)
- The UI will be titled "الملف الشخصي" (H1). Needs to be fully RTL compatible.

#### [MODIFY] [App.tsx](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/src/App.tsx)
- Add the `/dashboard/profile` route under the existing `ProtectedRoute` structure inside the dashboard routes block.

#### [NEW] [profile-navigation.md](file:///d:/%D9%85%D8%B4%D8%B1%D9%88%D8%B9/14-2-2026/2026-2-13/smart_performance_system/client/docs/profile-navigation.md)
- Write documentation on the implementation of the profile navigation as requested by the user, noting modified files and the added routes.

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
- Expand topbar user menu => click "الملف الشخصي" => verify navigation to `/dashboard/profile` and dropdown closing.
- Verify `ProfilePage` displays accurate information from the auth store context.
- Verify page back navigation returns correctly to the previous route.
- Confirm no new endpoints were added by checking network tab.
